Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.99,0:00:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I get words \Nmixed up and backwards, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so it can be kind of challenging. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So do I like reading? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I find books not interesting and boring.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.83,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I just get completely distracted.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to mentally prepare myself to read \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.04,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because there are so many things \Nyou could be doing.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t enjoy reading, \Nbut I do like reading the Bible. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, \Nit’s more than a book.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s definitely worth it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people may say \Nit’s not relevant for today.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.94,0:00:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you do look into it, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there are things \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you can learn from all the time.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s helped me to think before I speak.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I find that I’m actually more concerned \Nwith other people\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,—their well-being, how they’re doing, \Nand looking out for them.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Bible reading \Nhas made me a better person.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives me a little push for the day.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My favorite book in the Bible \Nwould probably be the Psalms \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.63,0:01:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,because it’s easy \Nfor me to understand \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and it’s really interesting to me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The young people, \Nthey can go through jw.org \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and get the Bible\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,—several different copies of the Bible—\Nright there.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We’ll type in the certain— \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,that certain scripture \Nand there’ll be articles about it.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.02,0:01:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing I’m loving is the new videos\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,—an introduction to this book of the Bible. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It just takes two or three minutes \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can understand \Nwhat you’re about to read\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,—that book—\Nand that makes a huge difference.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I go by topics or what interests me.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I look for something that’s interesting, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.46,0:01:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that’s very— \Nthat touches me directly; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it just becomes an enjoyable process.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s very, very relevant, \Nand it’s very important. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can find happiness. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who doesn’t want that?\N
